## All 15 Free Anthropic Academy Courses

### 🟢 Beginner / Foundations Track

- **Claude 101** — How to use Claude for everyday work tasks and core features
- **AI Fluency: Framework & Foundations** — How to collaborate with AI effectively, ethically, and safely
- **Introduction to Claude Cowork** — Working alongside Claude on real files and projects

### 🔵 Developer Track

- **Building with the Claude API** — Full spectrum of working with Anthropic models via the API
- **Introduction to Model Context Protocol (MCP)** — Build MCP servers and clients from scratch in Python
- **Model Context Protocol: Advanced Topics** — Advanced MCP patterns for production deployment
- **Claude Code in Action** — Integrate Claude Code into your development workflow
- **Introduction to Agent Skills** — Build, configure, and share Skills in Claude Code
- **Introduction to Subagents** — Use and create sub-agents in Claude Code

### 🟡 Cloud / Product Track

- **Claude with Amazon Bedrock** — Working with Claude through AWS
- **Claude with Google Cloud’s Vertex AI** — Working with Claude through Google Cloud

### 🟠 Education Track

- **AI Fluency for Educators** — For faculty and instructional designers
- **Teaching AI Fluency** — For those teaching AI fluency in instructor-led settings
- **AI Fluency for Students** — For students using AI to boost learning and career planning

### 🔴 Mission-Driven Track

- **AI Fluency for Nonprofits** — For nonprofit professionals increasing organizational impact

